97
00:05:29,504 --> 00:05:30,471
-Good luck, Misa Misa!

98
00:05:30,504 --> 00:05:31,871
MISA (VOICEOVER):
Way to go, Motchi.

99
00:05:31,904 --> 00:05:33,271
You're a natural.

100
00:05:33,304 --> 00:05:36,038
-I'll be here ready to celebrate
when they decide to hire you!

101
00:05:39,738 --> 00:05:41,438
I don't think I'm
cut out for this.

102
00:05:45,571 --> 00:05:46,871
