103
00:05:46,904 --> 00:05:49,838
I don't believe you and I
have met before, have we Miso?

104
00:05:49,871 --> 00:05:51,204
My name is John Wallace.

105
00:05:51,238 --> 00:05:54,104
I'm the executive adviser for
the advertising department.

106
00:05:54,138 --> 00:05:54,938
Nice to meet you.

107
00:05:54,971 --> 00:05:55,804
-Thank you!

108
00:05:55,838 --> 00:05:57,904
I'm very pleased
to meet you too!

109
00:05:57,938 --> 00:05:59,771
-Well, this might seem
a little bit sudden,

110
00:05:59,804 --> 00:06:01,638
but I'd like to be
honest with you.

111
00:06:01,671 --> 00:06:04,004
We've been talking about
it, and we've pretty much

112
00:06:04,038 --> 00:06:05,971
decided to hire you already.

113
00:06:06,004 --> 00:06:07,971
But before we make
it official, we'd

114
00:06:08,004 --> 00:06:09,271
like to clarify a few things.

115
00:06:09,304 --> 00:06:11,071
-Yes?

116
00:06:11,104 --> 00:06:13,471
-We've been doing a little
background check on you,

117
00:06:13,504 --> 00:06:15,271
and according to our
sources, a burglar

118
00:06:15,304 --> 00:06:16,904
killed your parents
during a robbery.

119
00:06:16,938 --> 00:06:19,604
You worship Kira because
he killed the suspect.

120
00:06:19,638 --> 00:06:21,604
Isn't it true that
you came to Tokyo

121
00:06:21,638 --> 00:06:23,938
in hopes of finding
and meeting Kira?

122
00:06:23,971 --> 00:06:25,471
-Uh, what?

123
00:06:25,504 --> 00:06:28,138
Who did you hear that from?

124
00:06:28,171 --> 00:06:29,504
-I'm afraid I can't answer that.

125
00:06:29,538 --> 00:06:33,138
The information is reliable,
and now I'd say it's confirmed.

126
00:06:33,171 --> 00:06:35,538
The look in your face tells
me that these are the facts.

127
00:06:38,138 --> 00:06:39,204
-Coil.

128
00:06:39,238 --> 00:06:41,738
I never thought you
investigated that far.

129
00:06:41,771 --> 00:06:43,138
-Also.

130
00:06:43,171 --> 00:06:46,171
You're still hiding something
from us, aren't you?

131
00:06:46,204 --> 00:06:49,171
Something you'd prefer
the world not to know.

132
00:06:53,671 --> 00:06:54,671
MISA (VOICEOVER): OK.

133
00:06:54,704 --> 00:06:57,771
Here's where I pause
and look nervous.

134
00:06:57,804 --> 00:06:59,904
-It seems you were
detained by the detective L

135
00:06:59,938 --> 00:07:01,671
for a short period of time.

136
00:07:01,704 --> 00:07:03,671
We'd like you to tell us
the full story of what

137
00:07:03,704 --> 00:07:04,971
really happened.

138
00:07:05,004 --> 00:07:07,238
It would be a problem if
the new face of Yotsuba

139
00:07:07,271 --> 00:07:08,904
turned out to be Kira.

140
00:07:08,938 --> 00:07:10,104
-Yes.

141
00:07:10,138 --> 00:07:12,771
We would appreciate it if
you were honest with us.

142
00:07:12,804 --> 00:07:13,338
-All right.

143
00:07:13,371 --> 00:07:15,171
I understand.

144
00:07:15,204 --> 00:07:18,438
I'll tell you everything.

145
00:07:18,471 --> 00:07:19,238
Yes.

146
00:07:19,271 --> 00:07:20,871
I was held for questioning.

147
00:07:20,904 --> 00:07:22,804
I didn't think it
was L, but he did

148
00:07:22,838 --> 00:07:25,971
ask me lots of
questions about Kira.

149
00:07:26,004 --> 00:07:29,204
But I'm not the second
Kira, and I never was.

150
00:07:29,238 --> 00:07:31,604
I was released because he
realised I didn't have anything

151
00:07:31,638 --> 00:07:34,038
to do with Kira after all.

152
00:07:34,071 --> 00:07:37,238
-Did you manage to see who it
was that was restraining you?

153
00:07:37,271 --> 00:07:38,171
-No.

154
00:07:38,204 --> 00:07:39,604
I was blindfolded
the whole time.

155
00:07:39,638 --> 00:07:41,738
-But if he asked you
questions, surely you

156
00:07:41,771 --> 00:07:43,704
heard his voice, right?

157
00:07:43,738 --> 00:07:45,738
-Only through a speaker
and voice filter, so--

158
00:07:45,771 --> 00:07:47,038
-Come on.

159
00:07:47,071 --> 00:07:48,238
What the hell is this anyway?

160
00:07:48,271 --> 00:07:51,104
A job interview or a
police interrogation?

161
00:07:51,138 --> 00:07:53,038
How long are we
gonna keep this up?

162
00:07:53,071 --> 00:07:54,504
I'm going to the bathroom.

163
00:07:54,538 --> 00:07:55,704
-He has a point.

164
00:07:55,738 --> 00:07:58,171
It seems the interview
veered a little off track.

165
00:07:58,204 --> 00:08:00,938
We're very sorry.

166
00:08:00,971 --> 00:08:06,104
Excuse me, but would you mind if
I went to the bathroom as well?

167
00:08:06,138 --> 00:08:08,738
This is getting exhausting.

168
00:08:08,771 --> 00:08:10,871
But everything's
going well so far.

169
00:08:10,904 --> 00:08:12,138
I just have to keep it up.

170
00:08:20,371 --> 00:08:22,804
REM (VOICEOVER): Being
touched by this scrap of paper

171
00:08:22,838 --> 00:08:25,571
alone will not restore her
memories of the Death Note,

172
00:08:25,604 --> 00:08:29,371
but at least now Misa
can see me once again.

173
00:08:29,404 --> 00:08:30,904
MISA (VOICEOVER):
What is this thing?

174
00:08:30,938 --> 00:08:33,538
Some kind of monster?

175
00:08:33,571 --> 00:08:34,671
-Misa.

176
00:08:34,704 --> 00:08:36,871
You're in a dangerous
situation right now.

177
00:08:36,904 --> 00:08:40,771
There are people within Yotsuba
who can easily have you killed.

178
00:08:40,804 --> 00:08:43,171
I've come here to warn you.

179
00:08:43,204 --> 00:08:44,938
Calm down and listen to me.

180
00:08:44,971 --> 00:08:46,104
MISA (VOICEOVER): Calm down?

181
00:08:46,138 --> 00:08:47,171
How can I?

182
00:08:47,204 --> 00:08:50,704
This thing looks like
it's gonna kill me.

183
00:08:50,738 --> 00:08:51,638
-Please believe me.

184
00:08:51,671 --> 00:08:53,104
I'm your ally.

185
00:08:53,138 --> 00:08:55,396
MISA (VOICEOVER): My ally?

186
00:08:57,171 --> 00:08:59,204
-Oh, man, I wonder if
Misa Misa's all right.

187
00:08:59,238 --> 00:09:01,104
Maybe we should've wired
her or used something

188
00:09:01,138 --> 00:09:02,438
to track her movements.

189
00:09:02,471 --> 00:09:03,971
LIGHT (VOICEOVER):
Just as I thought.

190
00:09:04,004 --> 00:09:06,704
The Kira before I was
detained and the one that

191
00:09:06,738 --> 00:09:07,938
surfaced afterwards.

192
00:09:07,971 --> 00:09:09,338
They must be two
different people.

193
00:09:09,371 --> 00:09:11,838
The MO clearly doesn't match.

194
00:09:11,871 --> 00:09:13,871
This Kira is killing
criminals as soon as they've

195
00:09:13,904 --> 00:09:18,171
had their crime broadcast on
TV, regardless of the situation.

196
00:09:18,204 --> 00:09:21,071
He's punishing people who
never intended to kill.

197
00:09:21,104 --> 00:09:23,671
Those who sincerely regretted
their crimes or people

198
00:09:23,704 --> 00:09:26,071
with excusable circumstances.

199
00:09:26,104 --> 00:09:30,171
To original Kira would've never
punished those kinds of people.

200
00:09:30,204 --> 00:09:34,971
That's the sort of distinction
I'd make if I were him.

201
00:09:35,004 --> 00:09:38,404
The way the original
Kira acted is

202
00:09:38,438 --> 00:09:40,104
disturbingly close to my ideals.

203
00:09:42,738 --> 00:09:45,804
What the hell am I thinking?

204
00:09:45,838 --> 00:09:47,104
I'm not Kira.

205
00:09:47,138 --> 00:09:48,571
Something's got to
be wrong with me

206
00:09:48,604 --> 00:09:52,304
if I'm seriously comparing
myself to that murder.

207
00:09:52,338 --> 00:09:55,538
-Light Yagami is Kira.

208
00:09:55,571 --> 00:09:56,504
Tell me.

209
00:09:56,538 --> 00:09:59,271
What is Light doing
at the moment?

210
00:09:59,304 --> 00:10:02,204
[mumbling]

211
00:10:07,571 --> 00:10:09,338
-Wha-- What are you?

212
00:10:09,371 --> 00:10:11,304
I mean, I can tell
you're not a stalker,

213
00:10:11,338 --> 00:10:14,238
but-- but you don't look
like a human at all.

214
00:10:14,271 --> 00:10:15,738
-No, of course not.

215
00:10:15,771 --> 00:10:18,938
I am a Shinigami.

216
00:10:18,971 --> 00:10:21,404
Before you were
captured by L, you and I

217
00:10:21,438 --> 00:10:22,638
worked closely together.

218
00:10:22,671 --> 00:10:24,338
-What are you talking about?

219
00:10:24,371 --> 00:10:25,804
I don't understand.

220
00:10:25,838 --> 00:10:29,671
You know me and Light is Kira?

221
00:10:29,704 --> 00:10:31,804
-The Death Note.

222
00:10:31,838 --> 00:10:34,904
It grants its owner the
power to kill someone simply

223
00:10:34,938 --> 00:10:37,071
by writing that
person's name in it.

224
00:10:40,538 --> 00:10:42,604
Light Yagami took
it upon himself

225
00:10:42,638 --> 00:10:45,338
to punish criminals
using that notebook.

226
00:10:45,371 --> 00:10:47,604
He soon became known
to the world as Kira.

227
00:10:50,871 --> 00:10:53,871
You also possess
that same power.

228
00:10:53,904 --> 00:10:57,738
In fact, your ability was
even greater than his.

229
00:10:57,771 --> 00:11:00,938
You managed to find
Light by using your power

230
00:11:00,971 --> 00:11:03,604
to determine that he
was, in fact, Kira.

231
00:11:03,638 --> 00:11:05,138
-Light is Kira?

232
00:11:05,171 --> 00:11:07,471
And I'm the second Kira?

233
00:11:07,504 --> 00:11:08,438
REM: That's right.

234
00:11:08,471 --> 00:11:11,171
Or rather, that
used to be the case.

235
00:11:11,204 --> 00:11:14,071
Light arranged it so you
would both lose this power.

236
00:11:14,104 --> 00:11:16,871
This was all
according to his plan.

237
00:11:16,904 --> 00:11:18,271
-He did?

238
00:11:18,304 --> 00:11:21,071
Then Ryuzaki was right.

239
00:11:21,104 --> 00:11:24,804
-Misa, do you still love
Light enough to die for him?

240
00:11:27,638 --> 00:11:29,671
-Unbelievable.

241
00:11:29,704 --> 00:11:31,338
You've got to be
telling the truth.

242
00:11:31,371 --> 00:11:34,304
You already know
everything about me.

243
00:11:34,338 --> 00:11:37,338
I totally believe you now.

244
00:11:37,371 --> 00:11:39,871
And yes, I do love him.

245
00:11:39,904 --> 00:11:41,171
To death.

246
00:11:41,204 --> 00:11:43,638
Not to mention how amazing
it is that Light and I were

247
00:11:43,671 --> 00:11:44,871
both Kira.

248
00:11:44,904 --> 00:11:46,638
Of course I'd want to
believe something like that.

249
00:11:46,671 --> 00:11:50,171
I only wish I could remember it.

250
00:11:50,204 --> 00:11:52,771
-You haven't changed, Misa.

251
00:11:52,804 --> 00:11:55,138
And it seems your
feelings for Light

252
00:11:55,171 --> 00:11:57,404
will never change, either.

253
00:11:57,438 --> 00:12:00,638
It's enough to convince me that
the only way you can be truly

254
00:12:00,671 --> 00:12:04,571
happy in life is if you can
support him in his plan.

